    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5; width: 100%;">Acts like an “autocomplete” for code, suggesting lines or whole functions as you type.</p>
  </div>

  <div style="flex: 1; background: #f2f4f7; border-radius: 14px; box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); padding: 18px 20px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; text-align: left; align-items: center;">
