    <h3 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.3; width: 100%;">AI Debugging</h3>
    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5; width: 100%;">Developers use AI to spot errors and recommend fixes.</p>
