  <div style="flex: 1; background: #f2f4f7; border-radius: 14px; box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); padding: 18px 20px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; text-align: left; align-items: center;">
 <p style="width: 50px; height: 50px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 10px; font-size: 2.5rem">🌐
 
 </p>
    <h3 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.3; width: 100%;">Website Builders</h3>
    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5; width: 100%;">Some tools let you describe a website in words, and AI creates the HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to make it real.</p>
